    <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-weight:300;margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.7;">Not a skills test. Not a knowledge assessment. A professional mirror — built for the collective future of L&amp;D and HR.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;">
      <div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#FFE600;">30</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Questions</div></div>
      <div style="width:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#FFE600;">5</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Behaviours</div></div>
      <div style="width:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);"></div>
      <div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#FFE600;">8–10</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Minutes</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6B7B6A;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px;font-style:italic;">Thirty questions across five courage behaviours. Allow yourself eight to ten minutes of quiet, honest reflection. The entire value of this diagnostic is in your honesty with yourself.</p>
  <button class="btn-primary" onclick="start()">Begin the Diagnostic →</button>
</div>

<!-- DIAGNOSTIC -->
